            "text": "(Marijuana Moment) — “The United States has not simply failed in how we carried out the War on Drugs — the War on Drugs stands as a stain on our national conscience since its very inception,” [Rep. Bonnie] Watson Coleman, who is also the sponsor of a congressional resolution to condemn the drug war, said… “As we work to solve this issue, it is essential that we change tactics in how we address drug use away from the failed punitive approach and towards a health-based and evidence-based approach.”",
